build.xml	->  ANT Project   (Java)
				ANT Compiler
pom.xml		->  MAVEN Prject  (Java)
				MAVEN Compiler
				
				
Disadvantages of ANT:

1) Size problem - Libraries should be local inside project 
2) Single Project :
3) Version issue : 


Advantages of Maven:

1) Libraries can be in central 
2) Multiple project 
		icicibank.com
			netbanking
			creditcard
3) Version Standards:
	Branch - Developement 		-> SNAPSHOT
	trunk/master - Production	-> RELEASE



POM - Project Object Model.

GAV

G - groupID			Main Project Name -> com.icicibank
A - artifactID		Sub Project Name -> netbanking
V - version			SNAPSHOT
					RELEASE
 
MAVEN Life Cycle :

	clean  -> package -> install -> deploy
